        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>April 11<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1849</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Reverd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Your favr. of <date>9th</date> Ult was duly reced.<lb/> and be
                assured I have not been unmindful of your<lb/> valuable suggestions. All the points
                in your circular<lb/> are calculated to have an important bearing on the<lb/> future
                dignity and distinctness of our holy religion<lb/> but the congregation of which I
                am a member having<lb/> taken ground differing so widely from the views
                con=<lb/>=templated by the proposed convention I can see no pros-<lb/>=pect of our
                cooperation therefore cannot recom=<lb/>=mend a delegate being sent. And moreover,
                on<lb/> a former occasion when all the Israelites of the city<lb/> formd but one
                congregation, a similar suggestion<lb/> was submitted from
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> to a very full mee-<lb/>=ting when by an
                almost unanimous vote it was re=<lb/>solved that we could not coalesce. Still I am
                satisfied<lb/> the effort is a very laudable one and if the association can<lb/> be
                organized its measures must have a general and sater-<lb/>=tory influence. You have
                my earnest prayer for its early<lb/> consummation</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">You will please find enclosed twelve 25/100 the<lb/> amt. Of your
                a/c as stated and let me add that I entertain<lb/> no asperities towards
                    <persName>Mr. Hart</persName> or any other person who may<lb/> differ with me in
                opinion, and in future if you desire it I<lb/> will settle with him Very
                respectfully yours truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <persName role="author">Joshua Lazarus</persName>
            </p>
            <p>(charge the quarter to the next a/c)</p>
        </body>
    </text>
